# Life Flow — Architecture and Development Notes

This document stores technical notes separate from the official style guide.

## Current Project Approach

The final project is expected to be an interactive web-based data visualization built primarily with D3.js.

Possible technologies:
- D3.js
- HTML/CSS/JavaScript
- Python for data preparation
- PostgreSQL for data storage or exploration
- GitHub for version control
- GitHub Pages for deployment

