- scene4_problem.js
- scene5_resolution.js
- scene6_outro.js

## D3 Build Strategy

### Layer 1: Prototype Motion

Before attaching final data, build the visual motion system:
- dots or particles
- paths
- zones
- opacity changes
- labels
- transitions

### Layer 2: Attach Real Counts

Connect the motion system to actual data:
- total transplants
- waitlist size
- deaths while waiting
- organ breakdowns
- donor type

### Layer 3: Add Interaction

Possible interactions:
- organ toggle
- hover labels
- scene navigation
- donor scenario toggle
- bottleneck toggle

